definitions.definition: A person of higher rank or quality , especially a colleague in a higher position .

subdefinitions.definition: The senior person in a monastic community .
The head of certain religious institutions and colleges .

definitions.definition: A superior letter , figure , or symbol .
One who has made an original grant of heritable property to a tenant or vassal , on condition of a certain annual payment ( feu duty ) or of the performance of certain services.

main_definition: A person of higher rank or quality , especially a colleague in a higher position .
